snippet.title: The G20 Summit | What is it Exactly? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
🤖 Join the Master ChatGPT course: https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgpt
Learn to harness the power of ChatGPT to transform your life! 
Use coupon code: G40 for 40% discount! Offer only valid for the first 400 people. 

This year, India has taken on the important responsibility of hosting the G20 Summit, a gathering of the top 20 nations with global significance. The G20 is a platform where leaders come together to discuss a wide range of critical issues, including economics, trade, climate change, and sustainable development.India's presidency of the G20 Summit is a momentous occasion. As the host country, India has the privilege of shaping the discussions and setting the agenda, allowing it to advocate for its own priorities on the world stage. In this video, Dhruv Rathee provides insights into the history and workings of the G20 group, shedding light on how India can effectively leverage its role as the host of this year's G20 Summit to make a positive impact on global affairs.

snippet.title: G20 Summit Delhi Live: PM Modi receives world leaders at Bharat Mandapam
snippet.description:
#g20delhi #g20summit #g20india

India holds the Presidency of the G20 from 1 December 2022 to 30 November 2023. The theme of India’s G20 Presidency - “Vasudhaiva Kutumbakam” or “One Earth · One Family · One Future” - is drawn from the ancient Sanskrit text of the Maha Upanishad. The G20 was founded in 1999 after the Asian financial crisis as a forum for the Finance Ministers and Central Bank Governors to discuss global economic and financial issues. The G20 was upgraded to the level of Heads of State/Government in the wake of the global economic and financial crisis of 2007, and, in 2009, was designated the “premier forum for international economic cooperation”. The Group of Twenty (G20) comprises 19 countries (Argentina, Australia, Brazil, Canada, China, France, Germany, India, Indonesia, Italy, Japan, Republic of Korea, Mexico, Russia, Saudi Arabia, South Africa, Türkiye, United Kingdom and United States) and the European Union. The G20 members represent around 85% of the global GDP, over 75% of the global trade, and about two-thirds of the world population.

#g20news #g20 #g20leaderssummit

जी-20 देशों की दो दिवसीय सम्मेलन नई दिल्ली में आयोजन हो रहा है। भारत दिसम्बर 2022 से नवम्बर 2023 तक G20 देशों की अध्यक्षता कर रहा है। भारत के 30 से ज्यादा शहरों में G20 की बैठक हो रही है। G20 की स्थापना 1999 में हुई थी। G20 में 19 सदस्य देश हैं। G20 देश वैश्विक सकल घरेलू उत्पाद के 85 प्रतिशत हिस्से का प्रतिनिधित्व करते हैं। वैश्विक व्यापार का करीब 75 प्रतिशत हिस्सा इन देशों का है। इन देशों में दुनिया की दो-तिहाई आबादी रहती है

snippet.title: Mission Raniganj - The Great Bharat Rescue | Official Teaser | Akshay Kumar | In Cinemas 6th October
snippet.description:
MISSION RANIGANJ - The Great Bharat Rescue is inspired by a real-life hero, Late Jaswant Singh Gill, an engineer who led a challenging rescue mission to save trapped miners from a flooded coal mine. This edge-of-the-seat thriller highlights Gill's courage and relentless efforts, showcasing his resilience to overcome adversities. A race against time rescue mission starring Akshay Kumar and Parineeti Chopra in the lead with a talented ensemble cast - Kumund Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Pavan Malhotra, Ravi Kishan, Dibyendu Bhattacharya and Varun Badola to name a few.

Watch the story of Bharat’s true hero with #MissionRaniganj in cinemas on 6th October.

A Pooja Entertainment Production
Vashu Bhagnani Presents

localized.title: Mission Raniganj - The Great Bharat Rescue | Official Teaser | Akshay Kumar | In Cinemas 6th October
localized.description:
MISSION RANIGANJ - The Great Bharat Rescue is inspired by a real-life hero, Late Jaswant Singh Gill, an engineer who led a challenging rescue mission to save trapped miners from a flooded coal mine. This edge-of-the-seat thriller highlights Gill's courage and relentless efforts, showcasing his resilience to overcome adversities. A race against time rescue mission starring Akshay Kumar and Parineeti Chopra in the lead with a talented ensemble cast - Kumund Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Pavan Malhotra, Ravi Kishan, Dibyendu Bhattacharya and Varun Badola to name a few.

Watch the story of Bharat’s true hero with #MissionRaniganj in cinemas on 6th October.

A Pooja Entertainment Production
Vashu Bhagnani Presents

भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। दर्शन दो भगवान! 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

कंस का अत्याचार बढ़ चुका था, सभी लोग कंस से बहुत दुःखी थे। कंस के अत्याचार के कारण श्री हरी के पास सभी देवता जाते हैं और उनसे विनती करते हैं की वो पृथ्वी पर अवतार लेकर कंस के अत्याचारों से सभी को मुक्ति दिलाएँ। श्री हरी उनकी बात मान लेते हैं और कंस की बहन देवकी के आठवें पुत्र के रूप में जनम लेने की बात कहते हैं। कंस को जब यह आकाशवाणी सुनाई देती है की उसका वध देवकी का पुत्र करेगा तो वो उन्हें अपने पास कारागार में डाल देता हैं। कंस एक एक करके देवके के छः पुत्रों के जनम के तुरंत बाद मार देता है। श्री हरी देवकी और वासुदेव को दर्शन देते हैं और उन्हें कहते हैं की वो अब उनके आठवें पुत्र के रूप में जनम लेने वाले हैं और कंस का वध वही करेंगे। श्री हरी देवकी और वासुदेव को उनके पुनर जनम के तप के बारे में भी बताते हैं की उन्होंने तप करके श्री हरी को अपने पुत्र के रूप में माँगा था, इसलिए वो इस जनम में उनके पुत्र के रूप में जनम ले रहे हैं। देवकी और वसुदेव यह सब सुन कर श्री हरी को प्रणाम करते हैं। श्री हरी देवकी के गर्भ में अपने अवतार को स्थापित कर देते हैं।  श्री कृष्ण के जनम के बाद देवी माया प्रभु की आज्ञा से वासुदेव को अपनी माया से जगती हैं और कृष्ण को कंस से बचाने के लिए गोकुल भेजते हैं जहां यशोदा ने एक कन्या को जनम दिया था जो की माँ शक्ति थी। वासुदेव कृष्ण को टोकरी में लेकर चल पड़ते हैं देवी माया कारागार के सभी दरवाज़ खोल देती हैं और सभी सैनिकों को भी बेहोश कर देती हैं। वासुदेव कृष्ण को लेकर अपने साथ निकल पड़ते हैं रस्ते में वो यमुना नदी पार करते हैं तो बारिश होने लगती है। शेष नाग क्षीर सागर से आते हैं और श्री कृष्ण को बारिश से बचाने के लिए अपने फ़न को को फैला देते हैं। देवी यमुना जी भी जल का स्तर बढ़ा देती हैं और उन्हें रोक देती हैं और श्री कृष्ण से विनती करती हैं की उन्हें अपने चरण चुने का मौक़ा दे। श्री कृष्ण यमुना जी की प्रार्थना स्वीकार कर लेते हैं और यमुना जी कृष्ण के चरण छूकर उन्हें प्रणाम करने के बाद नदी का स्तर काम कर देती हैं। वासुदेव नदी पार करके गोकुल पहुँच जाते हैं और यशोदा के पास लेती कन्या के साथ कृष्ण को बदल लेते हैं और वहाँ से वापस आ जाते हैं। वापस आने के बाद देवी माया वासुदेव को यह सारे वाक्य को मिटा देती हैं। जैसे ही भोर होती है बचे की रोने की आवाज़ से सैनिक वहाँ पहुँच जाते हैं और देवकी के आठवें पुत्र के जनम की जगह पुत्री की खबर कंस को देते हैं। कंस यह सुन वह पहुँच जाता है और उनसे पूछताछ करने लगता है। कंस देवकी से पुत्री को छिन लेता है और मारने कोशिश करता है माँ भगवती अपने असली रूप में आ जाती है और कंस को उसकी मृत्युु करने वाले के जनम हो चुका है ये बताती हैं, जिससे कंस बोखला उठता है। यशोदा नंदराय के घर में श्री कृष्ण जनम की ख़ुशियाँ मनायी जाती हैं।

snippet.title: கருத்தடை: இத பத்தி தெரிஞ்சுக்காம இருந்துறாதீங்க | Condom | IUD|
snippet.description:
Family Planning for Men: https://youtu.be/wEF7Y0G0UYY?si=1Xz9lag_Wyt67k9Q

Family Panning for Women: https://youtu.be/7BKrLAEl3_A?si=reNJo4Bvepbi8Eeq


In this video we've explained what contraception is and why it's crucial in family planning and reproductive health. 
Types of Contraception - Explore a wide range of contraception methods, including 
Hormonal Methods: Birth control pills, patches, injections, and implants. Barrier Methods: Condoms, diaphragms, and cervical caps.
Intrauterine Devices (IUDs): Learn about copper and hormonal IUDs and their effectiveness. 
Permanent Methods: Vasectomy and tubal ligation.
Emergency Contraception: Morning-after pills. Natural Methods: Fertility awareness-based methods and withdrawal. Effectiveness and Reliability - We'll discuss the efficacy of different methods, their success rates, and factors that may affect their reliability.
Benefits and Considerations - Explore the advantages and disadvantages of each contraception method, considering factors like convenience, cost, and side effects. Choosing the Right Method - Tips on how to select the contraception method that aligns with your lifestyle, health, and future family plans.
Access and Availability - Information on where and how to access contraception options, including healthcare providers and clinics.

Safety and Health Considerations - Discussing the importance of regular check-ups and consultations with healthcare professionals.

Remember, the choice of contraception is a personal one, and what works best for one person may not be ideal for another. It's essential to make an informed decision based on your unique circumstances and needs.

Share this video with friends and family to spread awareness about contraception and reproductive health.
 #theneeridaivelai #contraceptives

The 2023 US Open main draw runs from August 28 - September 10 in New York City at the USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center. It was both players' first US Open title, with Alcaraz winning his first Grand Slam title and Swiatek winning her third Grand Slam title. snippet.description: Here's everything you need to know about the new 2023 TVS Apache RTR 310 that has been launched at a starting price of Rs 2.43 lacs, whereas the top-end variant costs Rs 2.64 lacs (ex-showroom) The vehicle is available in three different colours - Yellow, Black and a special Blue. Though it shares its frame with the RR310 and BMW G310 R, the company has added a new aluminium sub-frame to lower its weight and has re-worked on its engine to make it faster and more powerful.

snippet.description:

People express their excitement and joy after watching the Shahrukh Khan starrer Jawan. Some people were seen adorning Shahrukh Khan's cut-out with flowers. Watch the video to check out what they said. Nayanthara and Vijay Sethupathi is also in the main lead in this movie. Also, you will see Deepika Padukone in cameo in Jawan Movie.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3871 | 8 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3871: Matki Phodne Ka Decision
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone in Gokuldham is looking forward to tonight's gathering at the clubhouse. Later, Champaklal chastises Jetha for continually being late to social gatherings, causing Jetha to appear on time. Madhvi and Bhide want Popatlal to be the chosen one since they recognize his desire to marry. Everyone becomes concerned when Bhide is late, and when he finally appears with a box in his hand, Jetha believes the matka has been broken. Bhide informs everyone that he has brought the matka in a box to protect it from harm. Popatlal attempts to keep an eye on the matka, but it slips out of his grasp.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3871, 8 Sep 2023

snippet.title: 'हर हिंदुस्तानी को फख्र' G20 Summit के लिए दुकानवालों ने सजाया Jama Masjid इलाका,लोगों ने क्या कहा?
snippet.description:
G20 Summit 2023: In preparation for the G20 Summit 2023, Delhi's streets were resurfaced, and once dark sidewalks were illuminated with new streetlights.The summit, scheduled for September 9-10, will be hosted at the state-of-the-art Bharat Mandapam Convention Centre at Pragati Maidan, a newly constructed exhibition center in the heart of New Delhi. This beautification project was aimed at showcasing India's cultural prowess and strengthening its position on the global stage. The G20 Summit is expected to attract world leaders from the globe's 19 wealthiest countries and the European Union. We dicussed about Delhi's security, Arrangemet and guests going to come. Watch the video to know about it.

#G20 #Delhi

snippet.title: How Bharat Mandapam Embodies India's Inspiration From Tradition And Pursuit Of Excellence
snippet.description:
#G20  #G20India  #G20Summit2023  #TajPalace #NewDelhi #PragatiMaidan #BharatMandapam 
The Hannover Messe in Germany, the world's largest convention center, has a storied history dating back to its construction 70 years ago during World War II. However, the global stage now turns to Bharat Mandapam in New Delhi, a cutting-edge and millennium-ready convention center. This architectural marvel will serve as the venue for the 18th G20 summit, showcasing the latest jewel in modern Indian design and infrastructure.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3870 | 7 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3870: Emergency Society Meeting
--------------------------------------------------------
At Gokuldham Society, everyone is looking forward to the Janmashtami celebrations. Anjali, Babita, and Komal discuss their specially created festive sweet delights. Abdul enters and announces that Bhide has called an emergency meeting for tonight to discuss the "Dahi Handi" ritual. Later, Madhvi enters and explains the cause of Bhide's urgent meeting. The wish-granting matka (earthen pot) presented by Tapu Sena Gor by a spiritual leader piques the interest of all the women. Popatlal accuses Bhide and Abdul of failing to inform him about the mystical matka. Everyone in Gokuldham is looking forward to Bhide's meeting and his announcement regarding the chosen one.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3870, 7 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1700000084/emergency-society-meeting-1000236833

The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. In this season, Baalveer is stripped of his powers, magic, and memories and lives as a regular boy Veer. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.

snippet.title: Launch of PSLV-C57/Aditya-L1 Mission from Satish Dhawan Space Centre (SDSC) SHAR, Sriharikota
snippet.description: Aditya L1 shall be the first space based Indian mission to study the Sun. The spacecraft shall be placed in a halo orbit around the Lagrange point 1 (L1) of the Sun-Earth system, which is about 1.5 million km from the Earth. A satellite placed in the halo orbit around the L1 point has the major advantage of continuously viewing the Sun without any occultation/eclipses. This will provide a greater advantage of observing the solar activities and its effect on space weather in real time.

snippet.title: New 2023 Tata Nexon Review - Positives, Negatives | AutoYogi
snippet.description: Here's all you need to know about the soon-to-be-launched 2023 Tata Nexon Facelift that has received tons of new updates including all-new exterior and interior. Though the platform and engine options remain the same, it's been updated to attract younger buyers who look for modern-age features in their car. While there are several big positives about this car, there are many misses/negatives too especially in the fit & finish department.

snippet.title: जन्माष्टमी के लिये धनियां पंजीरी व पंचामृत प्रसाद-Coriander Panjiri-Panchamrit Recipe 4 Janmashtami
snippet.description:
जन्माष्टमी पर बनने वाले पंचामृत व धनियां पंजीरी प्रसाद बनाने की विधि, panjiri kaise banti hai,prasad for gokulashtami,panjari bhog,recipe for panchajiri,charanamrit ingredients,
#vrat #janmashtami #panjiri #panchamrit 

Ingredients for
Janmashtmi Bhog Dhaniya ki Panjiri
धनिया - Coriander seeds - 1 cup (70 grams) 
मखाने - Fox nut - 1/2 cup
घी - Ghee - 3-4 tbsp
बादाम - Almonds - 15-16 no
काजू - Cashew - 15-16 no
खरबूजे के बीज - Muskmelon seeds - 1/4 cup
नारियल - Coconut - 1/2 cup, grated 
किशमिश - Raisins - 2 tbsp
इलाइची - Cardamom - 5-6 no, crushed
सफेद मिर्च - White pepper - 1/2 tsp
बूरा - Sugar powder - 3/4 cup

For Panchamrit
दूध - Milk - 1/2 cup
चीनी - Sugar - 2 tbsp
शहद - Honey - 1 tsp
दही - Curd - 1 cup
मखाने - Fox nut - 15-20 no
तुलसी - Basil leaves - 10-12 no




 
Subscribe for more recipes - 
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=nishamadhulika

http://www.youtube.com/nishamadhulika

-----------------------------------

𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐒:
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐰𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐚𝐠:
* Ghee(घी) - 1 Serving Spoon/60 Gram
* Edible Gum/Gond(गोंद) - 3-4 Tbsp/25 Gram
* Cashew Nuts(काजू) - 3-4 Tbsp/25 Gram
* Almonds(बादाम) - 3-4 Tbsp/25 Gram
* Dry Coconut(सूखा नारियल) - 100 Gram
* Melon Seeds(खरबूज के बीज) - 2 Tbsp/15 Gram
* Poppy Seeds(खसखस) - 2 Tbsp/15 Gram
* Fox nuts/Makhana(मखाना) - 2 Bowl/100 Gram
* Raisins(किशमिश) - 3-4 Tbsp/25 Gram
* Almondette Seeds/Chironji/Charoli(चिरोंजी) - 2 Tbsp/25 Gram
* Cumin Seeds(जीरा) - 1 Tsp
* Cardamom(इलायची) - 2-3 Pieces
* Black Pepper Powder(काली मिर्च पाउडर) - 1/2 Tsp
* Pistachios(पिस्ता) - For Garnishing

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐮𝐠𝐚𝐫 𝐒𝐲𝐫𝐮𝐩:

* Water(पानी) - 175 Gram

* Dried Coriander Powder(सूखा धनिया पाउडर) - 1/2 Bowl
* Singhada Atta(सिंघाड़ा आटा) - 1 Bowl
* Melon Seeds(खरबूजे के बीज) - Some
* Almondette/Chironji(चिरौंजी) - Some
* Lotus Seeds Pop/Makhana(मखाना) - Some
* Dry Coconut(सूखा नारियल) - Some
* Black Cardamom(काली इलाइची) - 1
* Cardamom(इलायची) - 2
* Raisins(किशमिश) - Some
* Jaggery(गुड़) - 1/2 Cup, Grated

𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐏𝐚𝐧𝐣𝐢𝐫𝐢, in a pan, put some Ghee & Coriander Powder. Roast it and take it out on a plate/Thali. In the same pan, put more Ghee & Singhada Atta, crushed Makhana, Melon Seeds, Grated Dry Coconut, Black and Cardamom Powder, Almondette/Chironji, and Raisins, and roast them well. Then put roasted Coriander Powder and grated Jaggery and mix it well. This way, Panjiri Bhog for Krishna will get ready.
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐃𝐫𝐲 𝐅𝐫𝐮𝐢𝐭 𝐏𝐚𝐠, keep the pan on the flame and put Ghee, Edible Gum/Gond, Cashew Nuts, Almonds, long chopped Dry Coconut, Fox Seeds, Melon Seeds & Poppy Seeds. Roast them separately then keep cooling down & crush them well. Then put Raisins, Almondette Seeds/Chironji/Charoli, Cumin Seeds, Crushed Cardamom, and Black Pepper Powder & mix them all well & keep them aside. 
For Sugar Syrup, take a pan, put Jaggery and water in it. Make one string of Sugar Syrup. Then put all the crushed & roasted Dry Fruits in the Syrup. Mix them well, put the mixture in a greased tray & spread it evenly. Garnish it with chopped Pistachios & keep it for drying for half an hour. Finally, cut it into pieces & enjoy!

ખટ પટ ના કરું તો ઊંઘ નહિ આવતી

હો વૈશાખ માં વિવાહ ને જેઠ કાઢ્યો મૈયર માં
અષાઢી બીજ ને આયો કોનુંડો પિયર માં
હો જવા દયો વાતો જૂની ફેંદો ના ગોદડાં
અવસરે જવું પડે છોડો હવે વેલડા

એ જાવું હોય તો જાજો હવે મૈયર નહિ આવું મેળવા
જીવ કેય ત્યારે આવજો નહિ આવું હવે તેડવા
મેલવા આવો તો હવે મારે મૈયર જાવું
નહીંતર કોનુંડો નથી મારે રમવું

એ ચમ આજ કરો છો આટલો લટુપણો...(2)
વાત મને હમજાય ગઈ છે બધી આજ

નકે વિચાર મોંડી વાળું હો રાજ

Lajo apne rishte ko nibhaane ki poori koshish karti hai, lekin aakhirkaar wo faisla leti hai Nikhil ko uske pyaar se milaane ka. Ab kya karega Nikhil? Kya wo Ishana se shaadi kar lega, ya Lajo ko apnaayega? Jaanne ke liye dekhiye 'Gustakh Dil'.
